cu.explanation_en: Setting tracking_area_code to 0 (a reserved value) will cause invalid TAC configuration and prevent proper network attachment.

du.explanation_en: Setting nr_cellid to a negative value (-1) will cause invalid cell ID configuration and lead to cell identification failures.
du.explanation_zh: 將 nr_cellid 設定為負值 (-1) 會導致無效的細胞 ID 配置，並導致細胞識別失敗。
